<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.4.2">
<l>eṉciṟuk kuṭṭa ṉeṉakkōr iṉṉamu tempirāṉ</l>
<l>taṉciṟuk kaikaḷāl kāṭṭik kāṭṭi yaḻaikkiṉṟā</l>
<l>ṉañcaṉa vaṇṇaṉō ṭāṭal āṭa vuṟutiyēl</l>
<l>mañcil maṟaiyātē māmatī makiḻntō ṭivā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Big Moon, our Lord, my little lad, a sweet nectar to me,</l>
<l>revealing [you] over and over with his little hands, he calls [you] by name,</l>
<l>if you desire to dance the dance with him who is the colour of kohl,</l>
<l>don’t hide in the clouds, come running joyfully!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
